    "The content underwent a rigorous validation process, which involved a panel of three judges with expertise in relevant fields: one medical student, one learning skills expert, and one nurse specialized in education.",
    "The validation process followed these key steps:1.",
    "Individual Review: Each expert independently evaluated the questionnaire content based on their specific area of expertise.",
    "This phase allowed for an initial assessment of clarity, relevance, and appropriateness of the questions, thereby ensuring that they are aligned with the study's objectives. 2.",
    "Collaborative Review: Following the individual assessments, a collaborative meeting was held with the authors and an expert panel."
